## Executive Summary

This comprehensive synthesis integrated findings from **4 research documents** totaling **3,353 lines** of analysis to create a **validated, production-ready migration blueprint**.

### Critical Corrections Applied

**Original Research Corrections (5):**

| Original Claim | Corrected Reality | Impact Severity |
|----------------|-------------------|-----------------|
| "HQ has Roundtable agent topology" | **MISLEADING** - HQ config has generic nature/animal template names (not Roundtable-specific) | 🟡 MEDIUM - These are template placeholders, not contamination |
| "HQ has Roundtable agent prompts" | **CORRECT** - HQ has NextNest prompts (mortgage-themed) | 🟢 GREEN - Accurate |
| "Roundtable missing 2 HQ scripts" | **REVERSED**: Roundtable has 2 scripts HQ doesn't | 🔴 HIGH - Script sync backward |
| "Response Awareness skills identical" | **DIFFERENT locations**: skills/ vs commands/ | 🟡 MEDIUM - Structural mismatch |
| "Enhanced 4 scripts from Roundtable" | 3 are NEW files (2,163 lines total) | 🔴 HIGH - Mischaracterization |

**Post-Verification Corrections (8):**

| Original Claim | Corrected Reality | Impact Severity |
|----------------|-------------------|-----------------|
| "NextNest root/subtree v1.0.0/v2.0.0" | **REVERSED**: Root is v2.0.0, Subtree is v1.0.0 | 🟢 GOOD - Safer than thought |
| "autonomous-workflow.sh upstream-ready" | **NOT ready**: Contains hardcoded Roundtable agent names | 🔴 HIGH - Removed from Wave 1 |
| "Standardize to maf-cli everywhere" | **Keep maf-nn** for NextNest (current state works) | 🟡 MEDIUM - Policy revised |
| "Enhanced scripts safe in Wave 2" | **Need backup/restore** before subtree pull | 🔴 HIGH - Risk mitigation added |
| "Memlayer dependencies work" | **BROKEN**: Scripts don't exist but referenced | 🟡 MEDIUM - Fix step added |
| "agent-startup.sh 1 dependency" | **3 specific lines**: 47, 273, 284 must update | 🟡 MEDIUM - More complex |
| "Total upstream: 2,263 lines" | **Corrected: 1,588 lines** (excluded autonomous-workflow.sh) | 🟢 GOOD - Less work |
| "Limited hardcoded paths" | **More widespread**: 10 hook scripts + multiple files | 🟡 MEDIUM - Audit expanded |

