## Immediate Next Steps

### Step 1: Review and Approve (Day 0)
```bash
# Review the unified blueprint
cat docs/plans/maf-franchise-migration-unified-blueprint.md

# Review repo-specific actions
cat docs/plans/repo-specific-actions.md

# Review upstream candidates
cat docs/plans/upstream-candidates-matrix.md
```

**Decision Points:**
1. Approve two-wave approach?
2. Approve Phase 0 (pre-migration validation)?
3. Approve upstream candidates (6 items, 1,588 lines)? - autonomous-workflow.sh excluded

### Step 2: Execute Phase 0 (Days -7 to 0)
```bash
cd /root/projects/maf-github

# Run path audit
find . -type f \( -name "*.json" -o -name "*.sh" -o -name "*.md" \) \
  -exec grep -l "/root/projects/" {} \; > /tmp/hardcoded-paths.txt

# Establish baseline metrics
find scripts/maf -name "*.sh" | wc -l > /tmp/baseline-script-count.txt
bash scripts/maf/spawn-agents.sh --dry-run 2>&1 | tee /tmp/baseline-spawn-test.txt

# Run readiness tests
# (Use test suite from unified blueprint, Part 2, Step 0.4)
```

### Step 3: Execute Wave 1 (Days 1-10)
**Day 1-2:** HQ structure cleanup + upstream 1,588 lines from Roundtable (autonomous-workflow.sh excluded)
**Day 3-4:** CI guard + health check
**Day 5-6:** Role-based support
**Day 7-8:** Session name standardization (per-repo: maf-nn for NextNest, maf-cli for others)
**Day 9-10:** Deploy to consumers

### Step 4: Pass Validation Gate
**Must pass ALL checks before Wave 2:**
- [ ] CI guards active and working
- [ ] Override order documented
- [ ] Health checks passing
- [ ] No agent failures for 3+ days
- [ ] Baseline metrics established

### Step 5: Execute Wave 2 (Days 11-28)
**Day 11-14:** Fix NextNest (canary)
**Day 15-18:** Update Roundtable (production)
**Day 19-21:** Clean up HQ
**Day 22-24:** Migrate to role-based agents
**Day 25-28:** Final documentation

