**Total:** 1,588 lines (not 2,263)

**Follow-Up Required:** Refactor autonomous-workflow.sh for role-based lookups (2-4 hours)

### Governance Framework

1. **Two-Wave Approach** - Validated as production-safe
2. **CI Guard** - Blocks subtree edits without `maf-upgrade` label
3. **Override Resolution Order** - 4-level priority system
4. **Role-Based Agents** - Mechanics global, identity local
5. **Health Checks** - Subtree integrity monitoring
6. **Validation Gate** - Must pass before Wave 2

### Risk Mitigation (Updated with Post-Verification Findings)

| Risk | Detection | Rollback | Status |
|------|-----------|----------|--------|
| Agent startup chain breakage | Test spawn before commit (3 lines: 47, 273, 284) | Restore agent-startup.sh | ✅ Documented |
| Topology schema incompatibility | Check version field (v2.0.0 root, v1.0.0 subtree) | Use v1.0.0 config | ✅ Documented |
| Subtree auto-detection failure | Test project root detection | Preserve detection logic | ✅ Documented |
| Session name chaos | Check all config files | Per-repo standardization (maf-nn for NextNest) | ✅ Policy revised |
| Missing memlayer | Check file exists (scripts don't exist) | Remove or fix references | ✅ Added fix step |
| Enhanced scripts overwritten | Backup before subtree pull | Restore from backup | ✅ Backup/restore added |
| autonomous-workflow.sh not generic | Check for hardcoded agent names | Exclude from Wave 1 | ✅ Removed + refactoring issue |
| Hardcoded paths break | Comprehensive path audit (10 hooks + scripts) | Use PROJECT_ROOT var | ✅ Audit expanded |
| CI guard false positives | Test label detection | Update array syntax | ✅ Fixed in blueprint |

